<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Scissors</title>
    <style>

        /* Reset default styles */
        * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f2f2f2;
        line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .container {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        }

        .error {
        color: red;
        }

        header {
        background-color: #333;
        color: #fff;
        padding: 20px;
        }

        nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        nav ul {
            list-style-type: none;
        }

        nav ul li {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-left: 20px;
        }

        nav ul li a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .hero {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 100px 0;
        }

        .hero h2 {
            font-size: 36px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .hero p {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        #longUrlInput {
            width: 80%;
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        #errorMessage {
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        button[type="submit"] {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 16px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        button[type="submit"]:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }

        #shortUrl {
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 16px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        #shortUrl:hover {
            border: 1px solid #007bff;
        }

        #shortUrl:focus {
            outline: none;
            border: 1px solid #007bff;
        }

        #qrCode {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        #qrCode img {
            width: 100%;
        }



        footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav>
          <h1>Scissors</h1>
          <ul>
            <li><a href="#">Features</a></li>
            <li><a href="/signup">Signup</a></li>
            <li><a href="./login">Login</a></li>
          </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <section class="hero">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Shorten your URLs with Scissors</h2>
            <p>Scissors is the easiest and fastest way to shorten your long URLs.</p>
            <p>Just paste your long URL in the box below and click Shorten.</p>
            <p>But first!, you have to create an account and login</p>
            <p id="shortUrl"></p>
            <div id="qrCode"></div>       
          <form id="shortenForm">
            <input type="text" id="longUrlInput" placeholder="Enter your long URL here" required>
            <button type="submit">Shorten</button>
          </form>
          <p id="errorMessage" class="error"></p>
        </div>
    </section>
    <footer>
        <div class="container">
          <p>&copy; 2023 Scissors</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
    
    <script src="script.js"></script>

</body>

    
</body>
</html>